# The Whetstone - Ollama Model Configuration
# Pro Edition: Qwen 3 14B (Q6_K quantization for best quality on 24GB RAM)
FROM qwen3:14b

# Context window configuration
# Qwen 3 supports up to 32k context, which is ideal for long philosophical dialogues
PARAMETER num_ctx 32768

# Temperature for philosophical discourse (slightly creative but coherent)
PARAMETER temperature 0.7

# Top-p sampling for nuanced responses
PARAMETER top_p 0.9

# Offload all layers to available accelerator (if any)
PARAMETER num_gpu 99